Class JsonResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.BasicNotifierImpl
      • org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.NotifierImpl
        • org.eclipse.emf.ecore.resource.impl.ResourceImpl
          • org.nasdanika.emf.persistence.JsonResource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Notifier, Resource, Resource.Internal
    public class JsonResource
extends ResourceImpl
    Loads EMF classes from JSON arrays using ObjectLoaders. Saving is supported if the resource content implements or is adaptable to Storable. The idea of this resource is to load models from manually created JSON files or JSON files generated by some other means, e.g. from MongoDB or REST calls.
    Author:
    Pavel
